Description:
ONLINE AUCTION TUESDAY 13TH OCTOBER AT 6PM!!
In order to bid during our online auction, you must register with one of our agents. Please contact us should you be interested in bidding.
If you would like to arrange an inspection of this property please contact our agent immediately to avoid disappointment. We have sold a number of properties virtually and there is every chance many more properties will sell during these restrictions.
Immerse yourselves in this well designed and recently renovated home which boosts tranquility and serenity - set in a peaceful side of Werribee and conveniently located minutes from the Princes Freeway, Werribee town centre, Eagle Stadium & Werribee Racecourse, Thomas Chirnside Primary School and public transport.
Wander through the front entrance and be welcomed by stunning floor boards that run throughout the entire home. Your senses will stir with what this property has to offer with no stone left unturned from front to back. The home consists of 3 spacious bedrooms all equipped with built in robes and are complimented by a central renovated bathroom with floor to ceiling tiles and a spacious living area. The renovated kitchen boasts great quality with beautiful bench tops, great bench space to impress any keen cook overlooking the dining area.
Step outside and be welcomed by a large backyard, side access with a large shed and ample room for potential subdivision (STCA) Set on approx 542m2 of land with no easements. - opportunities like this are few and far between.
Extras include Solar Panels, Split Air Conditioning, Gas Wall Heating and so much more! With nothing else to do but for you to move straight in.
We look forward to meeting you!

SOLD BY BURNSIDE AND BURNSIDE HEIGHTS #1 AGENTS Abi & Nivin
Team Abi from 361 Real Estate proudly presents to you this resort style property in the most desirable suburb of Burnside Heights.
This architecturally designed owner builder house is ideal for families, couples or singles who are looking for the complete lifestyle in a property.
The property features four bedrooms in total, an ensuite +2 bathrooms one of which is positioned to accommodate the indoor swimming pool
After a hard day at work or during a relaxing weekend why not spend your time at home either sitting by the fireplace, watching a movie in the theater, doing a workout in the gym or even having a dip in the undercover pool, no need to leave home when you have all these amenities in one place...your home
Lucky buyers can benefit from a relaxing convenient lifestyle close to walking trails Watervale shopping centre, CS shopping precinct, private schools as well as Kororoit Creek primary school catchment zone, public transport and parklands
Make a time and come and see for yourself.
As well as the up mentioned the property also includes:
• Double car garage with remote control plus a remote control gate for extra car space.
• Ducted heating, evaporative cooling
• Alarm system, intercom, ducted vacuum points, laundry chute
Inspection is highly recommended! Take advantage of this opportunity and call agents to organize an inspection today!!!

A Family Entertainer on a 447m2 block in a Superb Location !
9 Naracoorte Drive, Caroline Springs Vic 3023
Sitting on a 447m2 allotment beautifully positioned from a family perspective within easy walking distances to schools, local amenities like easy access to the Western freeway, Christ The Priest Primary School, sports and recreational facilities, Town Centre, this one of a kind home offers wonderful options for entertaining both inside & out in the desired suburb of Caroline Springs.
Comprising of:
- Master Bedroom supported with its own ensuite & walk-in robes for comfort living.
- 3 spacious bedrooms with built in robes.
- Central formal living area with plenty of natural light.
- Spacious central bathroom with separate toilet.
- Spacious kitchen with plenty of natural light with quality stainless steel appliances overlooking family dining & living area.
- Spacious backyard
- Mega closed shed for family entertainment.
Large sized laundry area with linen storage space, remote controlled double garage with internal access, centralized ducted heating, air-condition, downlights, blinds, separate central bathroom, and separate toilet.
This opportunity for a perfect home is not to be missed!

Description:
Titled And Ready To Build: Mt. Atkinson Estate Truganina
Ray White Truganina Proudly presents You this great opportunity to build your dream home, on this beautiful North facing 400M2 titled block of land in the highly sought after Mt Atkinson estate in Truganina.
Belong to Melbourne's new west at Mt. Atkinson, a brand new community in Truganina that will ultimately be home to up to 5,000 families.It's a place to call home, designed to deliver job opportunities and every aspect of quality living,including healthcare, education, connectivity, parks and amenities for an active lifestyle.
Just 25km from the CBD ,With easy freeway access, train stations and local bus stops nearby, Mt Atkinson connects you directly to the heart of Melbourne. This well-sized 400m2 (approx.) block of land in Mt Atkinson Estate is positioned in a prime pocket of Truganina in Melbourne's West.
The Melbourne Business Park at Mt. Atkinson will be a new commercial and employment hub for the region, delivering around 19,000 jobs in a well serviced, connected and attractive environment. The major precinct will give residents the chance to work close to home and provide business owners with the ideal space to grow and prosper, while the future town centre will also open up further employment opportunities.
Retail therapy will take on a new meaning at our future Westfield Town Centre. This exciting new shopping mecca will be a popular destination for everything from daily needs to the latest fashions, as well as dining and entertainment experiences. Healthcare and community services will also be available in this vibrant precinct.
Three quality schools will be delivered at Mt. Atkinson to nurture young minds, providing the perfect place to raise a family in a safe and friendly community. Plans for the community include a government primary school, private primary school and private secondary school, adding to the many educational facilities already in place in the surrounding area.
It is an address perfectly positioned for convenience and growth. A place where you will take pride in your community and where your neighbors will become your friends.
An opportunity like this is rare to come by and will not last long! To be a part of this exciting experience, living a balanced and active lifestyle at Mt Atkinson, please call Mark on 0425400600 to find out more!

Description:
Stunning, Designer, Esplanade Living!
You'll simply love the lifestyle, comfort, style & convenience that accompanies this designer, luxurious home which is sure to impress! Walk out to the tree lined park on your doorstep & stroll over to Lake Caroline only metres away!
*Comprising 3 generous bedrooms with built in robes/ optional 4th bedroom.
*Large master features fitted out W.I.R, luxurious ensuite with glass top vanity, floor to ceiling tiles & oversized shower.
*Striking timber tread staircase with glass & SS balustrading.
*Immaculate spacious kitchen with fantastic walk in butler's pantry, breakfast/meals bar, stone bench tops, soft closing drawers, quality appliances & plenty of bench & cupboard space.
*Adjoining meals & spacious family area opening up to a massive balcony overlooking the magnificent park & offers lake views.
*Study nook.
*Large laundry with bench & cupboard space.
*Double remote garage.
*Theatre/rumpus/home office with wet bar/kitchenette area (potential 4th bedroom) with skywalk connecting to main residence.
*Outside presents a low maintenance yard with artificial lawn & exposed aggregate concrete.
*Also featuring; ducted vacuum, 5 split systems, C bus electrical system, motorized blinds to family area, master bedroom & front door, alarm, camera system, video intercom, HDMI, Foxtel & data cabling throughout, high ceilings, external staircase, square set cornices & architraves.
*Within close proximity of all amenities Caroline Springs has to offer including Lakes, schools, shops, restaurants. West Waters Entertainment complex & CS Town Centre,
*Please call Nathan Hunt on 0409 853 503 to arrange an inspection or if you require any other real estate assistance!
(Photo ID is Required at all Open For Inspections)

Description:
LUMA Urban | Keon
Designed for modern family life, Urban homes combine the flexibility of open plan living areas with generous outdoor space.
Modern with a classic design, Keon is a versatile residence with the convenience of a carport accessed by a private rear laneway. Looking out to a lush rear garden, Keons spacious ground floor cleverly integrates kitchen and dining with light-filled family living and a convenient study nook. With plenty of space to entertain including separate rumpus room at the front of the home makes it ideal to retreat to for a movie or give the kids some space to spread out. Upstairs, generously sized bedrooms provide room to grow and plenty of storage, as well as a private outdoor terrace overlooking a landscaped front garden. Keon is a home designed for individuals to easily live together.
Premium inclusions include:
4KW solar panels with German Tech Sonnen battery system
Custom tiled patios and blue stone walk-way entrance
LUMA is a master planned Town Home community perfectly positioned with in the thriving Sunshine North location. With an abundance of open park land and a 3,600m2 central park large enough to host any activity.
FEATURES
Walking distance to Albion and Ginifer Train station
Easy access to the Western Ring Road
Minutes to Sunshine Hospital
15km to Melbourne CBD
Our sales office is temporarily closed but we are open online!
For further information we can be contacted on 8317 3725.
